      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve gotta check this beauty out! I have absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s in stunning shape, inside and out, and honestly looks and smells brand new. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look and fall in love!",
