    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, an apex of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated heritage. The S54 3.2L power plant features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain utilizes a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul. The factory suspension remains taut, preserving the chassis's legendary 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in a deep metallic, the bodywork exhibits factory-spec tolerances and luster. A true collector-grade example, it remains mechanically synchronized and aesthetically unblemished.",
      "price": 46500.0,
